article_title: Latest Official Figures Show The Obamacare Exchange Performance Was Worse Than We Thought

article_metadata.description: Now that we have final corrected figures on enrollments in the health Exchanges, it appears that 2014 calendar year Exchange performance warrants a grade of only C+ at best.
article_metadata.author: The Apothecary
